{
  "stem": "3341.4",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So when I, when I had a chance to talk, during the day, to a couple of the younger man which knew me-- and you know, the peasants in winter, they, they had to do some sort of work.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they usually carry the manure from the animals to the fields, and they put a big heap.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I started to talk in such a ways and if it will-- if the change over will be very bad-- because I told them you know, I know from other places, especially where I come from, when the German army retreated, they took all the able men and left only women and children.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that can happen here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said, really?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they're a primitive, simple people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I said, maybe we can hide outside in the field.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We will make a hiding place in the manure heaps and straw heaps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they said, yes, when it comes to that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I started to organize and said we should do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Luckily, the occupation was about two days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The second day was-- must have been a very big attack by Russian army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the Germans, in a in a hurry, they evacuated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They ran, ran away from that village, another 10 miles, or five kilometers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the next-- then we were free.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was actually hiding with the two fellows which I talked into-- I was already on the field.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said we are going to make the, the hiding place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we didn't do it physically.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we were there, considering it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And suddenly-- and there was-- the Germans moved out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we have seen it from the distance.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
